**Module File Structure Convention**
Maintain the following structure for each module:

```
src/
  module/
    module.service.ts              // Business logic and service functions
    module.type.ts                 // TypeScript types and interfaces
    module.hook.ts                 // Custom React hooks
    module_component.service.tsx  // UI-related services or components
  pages/
    module.tsx                     // Page-level component or entry point

sql/
  module.sql                       // SQL scripts related to the module
```

